## Gather Standard Errors for Plotting 
ses = read.table('ses.test.txt', header =T)

std_err = ses %>%
  gather("Type", "Value",-GeneSymbol)
std_err$c2 = paste0(std_err$GeneSymbol, std_err$Type)
colnames(std_err) = c("GeneSymbol", "Dataset", "Standard_Error", "c2")
